{"tid":1534192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我終於知道大家點樣可以做得更好","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T02:33:18.000Z","uid":314651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"79b8c7d7f504972648ce56006aa509bd0cfe4cd2","tid":1534192,"uid":314651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:32:14.000Z","msg":"帶定頭盔~以下真係新小說嚟架，唔好入我數，最多係暴力小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話說&ldquo;有個朋友&rdquo;係一個值嚟var<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係圖同片呀！</span></span><br />\n從前'有個朋友'打算整一套劣質3D戰術合作動畫,想麻煩手足sent一啲戰術片/行動方式我，'有個朋友'會盡快整出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下會將警察皆稱為曱甴屋，維權人士為（香港）聖戰軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />'有個朋友'極懶，有時間就整，可能最後都係吹水，反正宜家大難當前都無心情打機，幫到就幫<br />\n<br />\n資料方面，要市民馬路大街上站位，和理飛站位，路障整法，救人方式，排冰布陣，大街可利用最快整成or堆成路障以加固方法，未來希望係有系統學習同分工下可以<br />\n<br />\n四方八面突然一班街坊變身堆路障後曱甴走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，再放火魔法燒死班曱甴<br />\n<br />\n要求best路障建設方法為高，同連埋一難推開，難跨越<br />\n<br />\n另外亦要曱甴戰術及推進方式，推進間隔，如：大樓監察位，排位，指揮官位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n構思：曱甴推進完畢休息，未有新指令，但聖戰軍就連tg手機都唔洗望，綠手帶監察員一聲令下，由手帶顏色，黃色手帶人士一下擲出50幾個灌汽油水彈球，紅手帶人士為魔法師，一個火彈用彈弓，發出去，曱甴警喺可能<br />\n<br />\n一面（正面示威者同rb強化+777）（右面可能公路石膊）(左邊係海or大樓，最好唔係民居)後面7成都後油，<br />\n<br />\n燒死哂啲曱甴，大家都知曱甴裝唔防火，唔似消防哥哥安全，曱甴成身係油好易死架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n，就係咁街道就清潔哂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求比靈感加強本小說戰爭模式同內容，同埋睇得爽請幫推，有無精神病人士真係整出嚟就唔知啦，話說近排無打J好精神<br />\n<br />\n以上為小說內容，如有雷同純熟巧合，講埋係轉載先，真係告上庭，真係做9'有個朋友'都冇咁易<br />\n<br />\n我無話&ldquo;有個朋友&rdquo;係我，我係唔會驚架，唔好屈我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望未來有團隊整到，唔止得&ldquo;有個朋友&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n歡迎推加討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我P牌推唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說街坊袋入有一袋汽球同手帶，同揸車既人有汽油，都好正常啫"},{"pid":"17d66dbb910ebff9e7351fd81f05faa2f5c12e4a","tid":1534192,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"9月8！到時見！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2875c0a2a259c07d1805a7c865a10c6c42adfc04","tid":1534192,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:32:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=ba542add\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"dc8cb037c78617fe22581318543931a467952346","tid":1534192,"uid":285855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:33:13.000Z","msg":"借一下位, 純手動po請見諒<br />\n<br />\n侵侵叫大陸還清朝債卷<br />\n大陸唔肯還成10萬億美金<br />\n佢話前朝唔認佢要還<br />\n如果唔駛還唔認點解要還香港<br />\nbloomberg同台灣都有講, 點解香港無聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n如果借據美國買左我地係美殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-29%2Ftrump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=9b01df57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=36215437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7RnZZ8.png&h=a10eff3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"363e8110c7c4c58c37fb934080e15eaa685fe31c","tid":1534192,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8/9去美國領事館請願</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">派人道支援/過人權法</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3i9E9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3i9E9a.png&h=b678595e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M80cCFS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A